Package picasso.view.commands

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CombineEvaluator
    Allows the user to combine two expressions stored in history, and evaluates the result.
    Evaluater
    Evaluate an expression for each pixel in a image.
    FileEvaluator
    Evaluates an expression from a file
    HistoryWriter
    Saves an expression from the text box to a history file
    RandomEvaluator
    Evaluate a random expression for each pixel in a image.
    Reader
    Open the chosen image file and display in the Pixmap target.
    ShowHistory
    It displays the expressions in the history file in a user-friendly way
    Writer
    Save the chosen file.
